description:
OHEJP MEME 

 Standard Operating Procedure: This method describes the molecular identification of  Echinococcus multilocularis  DNA using a realtime PCR method with a 12s target and SsoFast probes. This molecular method follows on from the DNA magnetic capture fishing method described in separate SOPs with either manual or automatic washing protocols. 

 &nbsp;

